    <content><![CDATA[<iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width=330 height=86 src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=573131630&auto=1&height=66"></iframe>

<h2 id="基本常识"><a href="#基本常识" class="headerlink" title="基本常识"></a>基本常识</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">int [] arr &#x3D; new int[10];				  &#x2F;&#x2F;定义数组</span><br><span class="line">int [][]arr2 &#x3D; new int [2][2];</span><br><span class="line">int rows &#x3D; arr.length;					 &#x2F;&#x2F;行数,length没有()</span><br><span class="line">int columns &#x3D; arr[0].length				&#x2F;&#x2F;列数</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="类型转换"><a href="#类型转换" class="headerlink" title="类型转换"></a>类型转换</h2><p><strong>String</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; String to Array</span><br><span class="line">String s1 &#x3D; &quot;a,b,c&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">String [] strArr1 &#x3D; s1.split(&quot;,&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">String s2 &#x3D; &quot;abc&quot;</span><br><span class="line">String [] strArr2 &#x3D; s2.toCharArray()</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; String to Int</span><br><span class="line">String s3 &#x3D; String.valueOf(123)</span><br><span class="line">int num1&#x3D; Integer.parseInt(s3)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>Array</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">int [] arr &#x3D; &#123;1,2,3&#125;</span><br><span class="line">list &#x3D; Arrays.asList(array)</span><br><span class="line">int [] arr &#x3D; list.toArray()</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;List to Array</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; List initalization</span><br><span class="line">List&lt;String&gt; list &#x3D; Arrays.asList(&quot;abc&quot;,&quot;cde&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">String [] indexArr &#x3D;  indexList.toArray(new String[indexList.size()]);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="方法合集"><a href="#方法合集" class="headerlink" title="方法合集"></a>方法合集</h2><p><strong>queue</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">peek()			&#x2F;&#x2F;	返回第一个元素</span><br><span class="line">poll()			&#x2F;&#x2F;返回第一个元素，并在queue删除</span><br><span class="line">isEmpty()	add()	remove()	size()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>ArrayList</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">size()	.get(int index)		.add(element)</span><br><span class="line">isEmpty()	toString()	remove(int index)	remove(Object o)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>String</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">str.charAt(int i) .indexOf(&quot;object&quot;) .split(&quot;,&quot;) .length()</span><br><span class="line">.substring() .equals()	.trim()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>System.arraycopy()</strong></p>
<p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/361120/1583075124518-7deb469a-7bc8-4d77-b8d2-f548a570949f.png" alt=""></p>
<h2 id="循环遍历"><a href="#循环遍历" class="headerlink" title="循环遍历"></a>循环遍历</h2><h3 id="HashMap"><a href="#HashMap" class="headerlink" title="HashMap"></a>HashMap</h3><p><strong>keySet</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">for(String key:map.keySet())&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>entrySet():lterator</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Iterator&lt;Map.Entry&lt;String,String&gt;&gt; it&#x3D;map.entrySet().iterator();</span><br><span class="line">while(it.hasNext())&#123;</span><br><span class="line">Map.Entry&lt;String,String&gt; entry&#x3D;it.next();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>Map.entry&lt;&gt;</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">for(Map.Entry&lt;String,String&gt; entry:map.entrySet())&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &#x2F;&#x2F; entry.getKey()  entry.getValue()</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>map.values</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">for(String item: map.values())</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
